</blockquote>

<p>You know that old saying, if you always tell the truth you don‚Äôt have to remember what you told someone? Yeah, do that.</p>

<p>I‚Äôll ask a lot of follow-up questions. I‚Äôm trying to paint a picture of how you behave.</p>

<blockquote>
